Package model

Class Photo

java.lang.Object
model.Photo
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Photo extends Object implements Serializable
The Photo class represents a photo object, with values of caption, image path, last modified date, and a list of tags. This class provides methods to get and modify these value, as well as methods to add and remove tags. The class also implements the Serializable interface to allow for saving and loading Photo objects.
Author:
Shivam Patel and Neel Patel
